phrase: This mid-long ranged weapon is balanced for most conflicts.
translation: Dette midterste varierede våben er afbalanceret for de fleste konflikter.

phrase: Mecharii technology that can be charged multiple times to produce a more powerful beam.
translation: Mecharii teknologi, der kan opkræves flere gange for at producere til mere kraftfuld stråle.

phrase: Throw with left click and detonate with right click. On respawn, C4 are disconnected from you and must be shot to detonate.
translation: Kast med venstre klik og detonere med højreklik. På respawn er C4 frakoblet fra dig og skal skudt for detonere.

phrase:
This mid-long ranged shotgun packs a punch at longer distances.
Whilst scoping, its pellet spread will reduce by 70% over 3.0 seconds.
translation:
Denne midterste lange ranged shotgun pakker til at slå på længere dansere. 
 Mens scoping, vil dets pelletspænding reducere med 70% over 3,0 sekunder.

phrase: Place on a block surface to electrify passing enemies. Single use only.
translation: Placer på en blokoverflade til elektri og passerende fjender. Kun engangsbrug.

phrase: This mid ranged weapon launches Unstable Soltrium Cores that bounces before exploding.
translation: Dette MID Range Weapon lancerer ustabile SolTrium Corses, der springer før eksplosion.

phrase: This grenade has an Unstable Soltrium Core and detonates after 3 seconds. All players have two grenades, but enabling this will make your grenades stick to walls.
translation: Denne granat har en ustabil Soltriumkerne og detonerer efter 3 sekunder. Alle spillere har to granater, men det giver dig mulighed for at få dine granater til at holde sig til vægge.

phrase: Agaman technology that cuts through blocks instantly.
translation: Agaman-teknologi, der skærer gennem blokke øjeblikkeligt.

phrase:
This mid ranged weapon has a large clip for suppresive fire.
Overheats after 50 continuous shots
translation:
Dette mellemrum har et stort klip til undertrykkende ild. 
 Overophedninger efter 50 kontinuerlige skud

phrase: Agaman technology that fires balls of plasma in quick succession.
translation: Agaman-teknologi, der brænder bolde af plasma i hurtig rækkefølge.

phrase: Destructive Agaman technology that converts Soltrium energy into an explosive ball of plasma.
translation: Destruktive Agaman-teknologi, der konverterer SolTrium Energy til en eksplosiv kugle af plasma.

phrase: This close-mid ranged weapon shoots quickly but has a small magazine.
translation: Dette nærmideområde skyder hurtigt, men har et lille magasin.

phrase: Light Agaman technology. Fast firing, hard hitting.
translation: Lys agaman teknologi. Hurtig fyring, hårdt rammer.

phrase: Heavy Agaman technology. Fires a hard-hitting ball of plasma.
translation: Tung agamanteknologi. Brande til hårdt ramt af plasma.

phrase: This long ranged weapon uses magnetic propulsion and can be equipped with a 4x scope to provide support to allies at range.
translation: Dette lange varierede våben bruger magnetisk fremdrift og kan udstyres med 4x omfang for at yde støtte til allierede i rækkevidde.

phrase: This hard-hitting close ranged weapon contains a powerful Soltrium Core.
translation: Dette hårdt rammer tætte våben indeholder til kraftig Soltriumkerne.

phrase: Such a small gun. Such a massive boom.
translation: Sådan til lille pistol. Sådan en massiv boom.

phrase: This long ranged weapon uses Soltrium Propulsion technology to launch explosive missiles.
translation: Dette lange varierede våben bruger SolTrium fremdriftsteknologi til at starte eksplosive missiler.

phrase:
Launches a floating scanning orb that pulses every two seconds, revealing enemies through walls.
Scanner orbs can be shot by enemy players.
translation:
Lancerer flydende scanning orb, der impulerer hvert andet sekund, afslører fjender gennem vægge. 
 Scanner Orbs kan blive skudt af fjendens spillere.

phrase: This close ranged weapon creates a blast of shrapnel.
translation: Dette tætte våben skaber til blast af shrapnel.

phrase: This close-mid ranged weapon packs a punch. Watch out for the recoil.
translation: Denne tætte mellemrumspakker til at slå. Pas på samlingen.

phrase: Place block structures with this tool.
Attaches to walls. Right click to pull the wall down.
translation: Fastgøres til vægge. Højreklik for at trække væggen ned.

phrase: While inexperienced, this mercenary braved the journey to the Soltrium galaxy and seeks to prove their worth in battle.
translation: Mens det er uerfaren, bravede denne lejesoldat rejsen til Soltrium Galaxy og søger at give deres værd i kamp.

phrase: This solo operative seeks nothing but victory when it comes to saving their race from destruction.
translation: Denne solo operative søger intet andet end sejr, når det kommer til at redde deres race fra ødelæggelse.

phrase: A deadly sniper at range and a swift killer up close, they are capable of holding their own in any encounter.
translation: En dødelig snigskytter på rækkevidde og en hurtig morder tæt på, de er i stand til at holde deres egne i ethvert møde.

phrase: This commander lost their arm during the Flare but continues to fight for the future of their race.
translation: Denne kommandant mistede deres arm under flare, men fortsætter med at kæmpe for fremtiden for deres race.

phrase: Outlaws that roam the outskirts of the galaxy, attacking anyone that dares travel alone.
translation: Outlaws, der strejfer udkanten af ​​galaksen, angriber enhver, der tør rejser alene.

phrase: This Agaman fought vigilantly on the frontlines to prove their worth of entering the Soltrium galaxy.
translation: Denne Agaman kæmpede årligt på frontlinjerne for at give deres værd at komme ind i SolTriumgalaksen.

phrase: This Agaman gave up everything to make the journey to the Soltrium galaxy.
translation: Denne Agaman gav op på alt for at gøre rejsen til SolTrium Galaxy.

phrase: This Agaman highborn was infused with Soltrium in an experiment to produce an unstoppable mix of flesh and machine.
translation: Denne Agaman Highborn blev infunderet med soltrium i et forsøg for at producere en ustoppable blanding af kød og maskine.

phrase: Click the Play tab when you are ready
translation: Klik på fanen Afspil, når du er klar
Tryk på Escape for at annullere

phrase: A shadow market has developed at the outskirts of the galaxy where Soltrium is wagered. It's all or nothing in the arena where contestants fight for profit and survival.
translation: Et skygge marked har udviklet sig i udkanten af ​​galaksen, hvor soltrium er satset. Det er alt eller intet i arenaen, hvor refirmunanter kæmper for fortjeneste og overlevelse.

phrase: Start with nothing and collect weapons to eliminate the enemy team.
translation: Start med ingenting og saml våben for at fjerne fjendens hold.

phrase: All players start with the same randomised loadout.
translation: Alle spillere starter med den samme randomiserede loadoutout.

phrase: Soltrium is scattered throughout the outer sector. Various
translation: SolTrium er spredt i hele den ydre sektor. Forskellige

phrase: battalions have been dispatched to search for and collect the precious resource.
translation: Bataljoner er blevet sendt for at søge efter og indsamle den dyrebare ressource.

phrase: Get two kills with every weapon, then melee to win
translation: Få to dræber med hvert våben, så melee til at vinde

phrase: Hold the most Soltrium to win
translation: Hold det mest soltrium for at vinde

phrase: Weapons and Mods spawn around the map
translation: Våben og mods spawn omkring kortet

phrase: To reveal enemy positions to teammates
translation: At afsløre fjendens positioner til holdkammerater

phrase: Maps you have subscribed to in the workshop will appear here. You may need to refresh multiple times after subscribing to a new map for the list to update fully.
translation: Kort, du har abonneret på i værkstedet, vil beeatere her. Du skal muligvis opdatere flere gange efter at have abonneret på et nyt kort for listen for at opdatere fuldt ud.

phrase: Uploading map to the Steam Workshop
Double XP + Proton Weekend! Ends in
translation: Double XP + Proton Weekend! Slutter i.

phrase: This game mode is called Salvage. Two teams contest a canister that contains a valuable resource called Soltrium.
translation: Denne spiltilstand er bjærgning kaldet. To holdkonkurrence til beholder, der indeholder værdifuld ressource kaldet SolTrium.

phrase: The team with the most players near the canister will extract Soltrium and earn points for their team. This can be seen at the top of the screen.
translation: Holdet med de fleste spillere i nærheden af ​​beholderen vil udtrække SolTrium og tjene point for deres hold. Dette kan ses øverst på skærmen.

phrase: When a canister is depleted, a new one will spawn elsewhere. The first team to reach 500 points wins!
translation: Når en beholder er udtalt, vil den nye vil gyde andetsteds. Det første hold for at nå 500 point vinder!

phrase: Ammo Bonuses drop when a player dies. Pick them up to get extra ammo for your weapons and earn 2 points for your team.
translation: Ammo Bonuses Drop Wheen til Player Dies. Vælg dem for at få ekstra ammunition til dine våben og tjen 2 point for dit team.

phrase: This game mode is called Breakthrough. To win, your team must control all five zones.
translation: Denne spiltilstand kaldes gennembrud. For at vinde skal dit hold styre alle fem zoner.

phrase: When a zone is captured by your team, it will be frozen for up to 20 seconds. While frozen the enemy cannot retake it, which gives your team the chance to push forward into the next zone.
translation: Når en zone er afkortet af dit hold, vil den blive frosset i op til 20 sekunder. Mens frosne fjenden kan ikke genoptage det, hvilket giver dit hold mulighed for at skubbe frem til den næste zone.

phrase: Zones must be captured in order and cannot be back-capped.
translation: Zoner skal fanges i rækkefølge og kan ikke back-capped.

phrase: This game mode is called Control Shift. There is one zone and the objective is to push that zone all the way back into enemy territory.
translation: Denne spiltilstand hedder Control Shift. Der er en zone, og målet er at skubbe den zone hele vejen tilbage til fjendens territorium.

phrase: The zone will begin moving when one team has more players inside it than the other.
translation: Zonen begynder at flytte, når et hold har flere spillere inde i det end det andet.

phrase: This game mode is called Escort. To win, your team must deliver 3 bombs.
translation: Denne spiltilstand hedder Escort. For at vinde, skal dit hold levere 3 bomber.

phrase: Each team has a bomb that they must pick up from their side of the map and deliver to the enemy bomb site.
translation: Hvert hold har en bombe, som de skal afhente fra deres side af kortet og levere til fjendens bombe site.

phrase: You can either escort your bomb carrier, or defend your bomb site from the enemy.
translation: Du kan enten eskortere din bombeholder eller forsvare dit bombewebsted fra fjenden.

phrase: This game mode is called Capture the Flag. Each team has a flag that they must defend.
translation: Denne spiltilstand hedder Capture Flag. Hvert hold har flag, som de skal forsvare.

phrase: To win your team must steal the enemy flag and take it back to your base 3 times.
translation: For at vinde dit hold skal stjæle fjendens flag og tage det tilbage til din base 3 gange.

phrase: You can either infiltrate the enemy base, or defend your flag from the enemy.
translation: Du kan enten infiltrere fjendens base, eller forsvare dit flag fra fjenden.

phrase: This game mode is called Gun Game. Each player starts with the same weapon and progresses to the next weapon after getting 2 kills.
translation: Denne spiltilstand hedder pistolspil. Hver spiller starter med samme våben og skrider frem til det næste våben efter at have fået 2 dræber.

phrase: The stage that each player is up to is shown at the top of the screen.
translation: Det stadium, som hver spiller er op til, vises øverst på skærmen.

phrase: To win you must advance to Stage 11 and then kill an enemy with either your digger or your knife.
translation: For at vinde skal du gå videre til Stage 11 og derefter dræbe en fjende med enten din digger eller din kniv.

phrase: When dying to fall damage or an enemy digger/knife, you will be sent back one stage.
translation: Når du dør for at falde skade eller en fjende digger / kniv, vil du blive sendt tilbage et stadium.

phrase: This free-for-all game mode is called Head Hunter. To win, you must hold the most Soltrium when the timer runs out.
translation: Denne gratis-for-alle spiltilstand hedder Head Hunter. For at vinde, skal du holde det mest soltrium, når timeren løber ud.

phrase: Each player starts with nothing and collects weapons and mods from around the map.
translation: Hver spiller starter med ingenting og samler våben og mods fra hele kortet.

phrase: When a player dies, they will drop their weapons, half their Soltrium and half their mods.
translation: Når en spiller dør, vil de ned afspiller, halvdelen af ​​deres soltrium og halvdelen af ​​deres mods.

phrase: Pick up Soltrium to win, but be careful as the player with the most Soltrium will be revealed to everyone.
translation: Pick up Solrium for at vinde, men pas på, da spilleren med det mest soltrium vil blive åbenbaret for alle.

phrase: This arena game mode is called Spire. To win, you must eliminate the enemy team 5 times.
translation: Denne arena spiltilstand hedder Spire. For at vinde, skal du eliminere fjendens hold 5 gange.

phrase: Each player starts with nothing and must build into the sky to pick up weapons.
translation: Hver spiller starter med ingenting og skal bygge ind i himlen for at afhente våben.

phrase: This arena game mode is called Static. To win, you must eliminate the enemy team 5 times.
translation: Denne arena spiltilstand hedder statisk. For at vinde, skal du eliminere fjendens hold 5 gange.

phrase: Each player shares the same loadout, which is randomised each round.
translation: Hver spiller deler samme loadout, som er randomiseret hver runde.
Tryk på plads for at fortsætte
Ændre til struktur for at fortsætte

phrase: Head over to the shooting range
Select a weapon from the gun rack
Shoot the targets and try different weapons. Press
translation: Skyd målene og prøv forskellige våben. Trykke

phrase: Protons, XP and stats will not be tracked
translation: Protoner, XP og statistikker vil ikke blive sporet

phrase: in chat to set your spawn point
translation: i chat for at sætte dit gydepunkt

phrase: Weapon cooldowns removed. Players are invincible
Note - claiming the lobby will restart the round
translation: Bemærk - hævder lobbyen vil genstarte runden

phrase: Note - changing these settings will restart the round
translation: Bemærk - Ændring af disse indstillinger genstarter runden

phrase: An update is available. Close the game and update the game through
translation: En opdatering er tilgængelig. Luk spillet og opdater spillet igennem
Mislykkedes. Online spil er ikke tilgængelig

phrase: Show Enemies on the Zone Bar
Spend more time on the CPU producing higher quality world meshes, which reduces pressure on the GPU.
translation: Brug mere tid på CPU'en, der producerer højere kvalitet verdens masker, hvilket reducerer pres på GPU'en.

phrase: The game will automatically disable effects and lower postprocessing quality to keep FPS high. It may take up to one minute to determine optimal rendering settings.
translation: Spillet vil automatisk deaktivere effekter og lavere efterprocessingkvalitet for at holde FPS høj. Det kan tage op til et minut at bestemme optimale gengivelsesindstillinger.

phrase: Changes how often you receive player data from the server. Lower this value if you are on unstable or low-bandwidth internet.
translation: Ændrer, hvor ofte du modtager afspilningsdata fra serveren. Sænk denne værdi, hvis du er på ustabil eller lavt båndbredde internet.

phrase: Must keep enabled at all times
The size of the bottom-right minimap
The internal scale of the bottom-right minimap
translation: Den indre skala af nederste højre minimap

phrase: The server name will not be displayed on the scoreboard and other player names and levels will be randomised for you.
translation: Servernavnet vises ikke på resultattavlen, og andre afspillernavne og niveauer vil blive randomiseret til dig.

phrase: Controls whether the in-game HUD is rendered. Shortcut:
translation: Kontrollerer, om HUD's in-game er gengivet. Genvej:

phrase: Controls whether the chat is rendered. Shortcut:
translation: Kontrollerer, om chatten er gengivet. Genvej:

translation: Kontrollerer, om killfeedet er gengivet. Genvej:

translation: Kontrollerer, om spillernavne er gengivet. Genvej:

phrase: Particles are produced when objects are hit or destroyed. Lowering this percentage will increase FPS
translation: Partikler fremstilles, når objekter rammes eller ødelægges. Sænkning af denne procentdel vil øge FPS

phrase: The map is divided into chunks of 32x32x32 blocks. Reducing this will increase FPS
translation: Kortet er opdelt i klumper på 32x32x32 blokke. Reduceret dette vil øge FPS

phrase: The world is illuminated by sun lights, block lights and muzzle flashes from guns. Reducing the maximum amount of lights that can be rendered will increase FPS
translation: Verden er belyst af sollys, bloklys og næseblinker blinker fra våben. Reducting den maksimale mængde lys, der kan gengives, vil øge FPS

phrase: Frames per Second (FPS) is the amount of times the game will update each second. Lowering this value will decrease CPU and GPU usage
translation: Rammer per sekund (FPS) er mængden af ​​gange, hvor spillet vil opdatere hvert sekund. Sænkning af denne værdi vil reducere CPU og GPU brug

phrase: Screen Space Ambient Occlusion darkens the crevices between objects
translation: Skærmrum Ambient okklusion mørkere sprækkerne mellem objekter

phrase: Bloom increases and blurs the brightness of emissive surfaces
translation: Bloom forbløffer og blurserer lysstyrken af ​​emissive overflader

phrase: Crepuscular rays are shafts of lights that originate from a star
translation: Twilight stråler er aksler af lys, der stammer fra en stjerne

phrase: Parts of the map will be darkened by the shadows cast from other objects
translation: Dele af kortet bliver mørkere af skyggerne kastet fra andre objekter

phrase: Controls whether players from casting shadows
translation: Kontrollerer, om spillere fra Casting Shadows

phrase: Controls whether Disruptors, C4, Scanners and Canisters cast shadows
translation: Kontrollerer om forstyrrelser, C4, scannere og beholdere kastede skygger

phrase: Controls whether leaf particles cast shadows
Controls whether falling structures cast shadows
translation: Kontrollerer om faldende strukturer støbte skygger

phrase: Multisampling smooths the edges of objects
The Bare Minimum rendering mode skips all postprocessing and renders objects directly to the screen. Disabling this may take some time
translation: Den bare minimale gengivelsesmodus springer alle postprocessering og gør indsigere direkte til skærmen. Deaktivering dette kan tage lidt tid

phrase: With Bare Minimum enabled, this controls whether the region around 2X and 4X scopes is blurred or black
translation: Med bare minimum aktiveret, kontrollerer dette, om regionen omkring 2x og 4x scopes er sløret eller sort

phrase: Compressing textures will use less memory on the GPU but the game will take longer to start up
translation: Komprimering af teksturer vil bruge mindre hukommelse på GPU, men spillet vil tage længere tid at starte op

phrase: Debug logging stores log files in the AppData/Roaming/Vercidium/log folder, which helps the developers fix bugs and crashes
translation: DEBUG LOGKING Gemmer Logfiler i AppData / Roaming / Vercidium / Log-mappen, som hjælper udviklerne med at løse bugs og nedbrud

phrase: Safe Mode prevents crashes from closing the game, but may slow the game down slightly
translation: Sikker tilstand forhindrer nedbrud i at lukke spillet, men kan sænke spillet lidt ned

phrase: Vertical sync matches the update rate of the game to the refresh rate of your monitor. Enabling this may fix screen tearing
translation: Lodret synkronisering matcher opdateringshastigheden for spillet til opdateringshastigheden på skærmen. Aktivering af dette kan rette skærmen rive

phrase: Dynamic Exposure mimics the human eye by adjusting exposure based on the brightness of the scene
translation: Dynamisk eksponering efterligner det menneskelige øje ved at justere eksponeringen baseret på scenens lysstyrke

phrase: Reducing the quality of shadows will increase FPS but cause close-up shadows to flicker
translation: Reduktion Kvaliteten af ​​skyggerne vil øge FPS, men forårsager nærbillede skygger til flimmer

phrase: Reducing the quality of lighting will increase FPS but pixelate lighting
translation: Reduktion Kvaliteten af ​​belysningen vil øge FPS Butpixelate Lighting

phrase: Enabling this will remove parts of the rendering pipeline that are potentially slow on older hardware
translation: Aktivering af dette vil fjerne dele af gengivelsesrørledningen, der potentielt er langsomt på ældre hardware

phrase: Enable this if you are having trouble connecting to servers
translation: Aktivér dette, hvis du er Havir Troublon, der forbinder til servere

phrase: If enabled, the scroll wheel will only rotate between your weapons and not your building/digging tools
translation: Hvis det er aktiveret, drejer rullehjulet kun mellem dine våben og ikke dine Building / Digging Tools

phrase: If enabled, each Ironsight / 2X / 4X Sensitivity option is a multiplier based on your Look Sensitivity
translation: Hvis aktiveret, er hver Ironight / 2x / 4x følsomhed mulighed for en multiplikator baseret på din look-følsomhed

phrase: The amount of sections of the map that are updated each frame. Lowering this will reduce CPU usage
translation: Mængden af ​​sætninger af kortet, der opdateres hver ramme. Sænkning dette vil reducere CPU-brug

phrase: Enabling this will reduce texture resolution to increase FPS and reduce memory usage. Disabling this requires a restart to take effect
translation: Aktivering af dette vil reducere teksturopløsningen for at øge FPS og reducere hukommelsesforbruget. Deaktivering af dette kræver genstart for at træde i kraft

phrase: Increasing this will improve the quality of Ambient Occlusion postprocessing
translation: Forøgelse af dette vil forbedre kvaliteten af ​​omgivende indtjening efterprocessering

phrase: This controls how far away friendly names will show
translation: Dette styrer, hvor langt væk venlige navne vil vise

phrase: When disabled, the Midi/Digger/Structure will be skipped when scrolling weapons and pressing the Last Tool keybind will not swap to them
translation: Når deaktiveres, vil MIDI / Digger / Structure blive sprunget over, når du ruller våben og trykke på den sidste værktøjskastbind, ikke bytter dem

phrase: Automatically pause the game when you change to another window
translation: Pause automatisk spillet, når du skifter til et andet vindue

phrase: Replace swear words in chat messages with delicious food
translation: Udskift swear ord i chatbeskeder med lækker mad

phrase: Enabling this will make the game render at the resolution specified below and stretch to the size of the window
translation: Aktivering af dette vil gøre spillet til at gøre ved den nedenstående opløsning og strække til størrelsen af ​​vinduet

phrase: Enabling this will reduce the pixelation of lower game resolutions
translation: Aktivering af dette vil reducere pixellationen af ​​lavere spilopløsninger

phrase: Experimental performance setting, may crash your game. Don't enable if you haven't been told to
translation: Eksperimentel præstationsindstilling, kan kollidere dit spil. Aktivér ikke, hvis du ikke har fået at vide det

phrase: New rendering pipeline. Please let Vercidium know in Discord if the game runs faster/slower with this enabled
translation: Ny rendering pipeline. Lad venligst Vercidium vide i Discord, hvis spillet løber hurtigt / langsommere med dette aktiveret
